{"tid":1880593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藥房訛稱生理鹽水可消毒  兩人被捕","createTime":"2020-02-15T03:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T03:29:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5617fe804b8366ffd52e64d2ca3d2a030389d7d","tid":1880593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/A7UBGSWEK3OBXGRNAO7CPHIMF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FA7UBGSWEK3OBXGRNAO7CPHIMF4%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNiVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=9a3a1d1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200215%2FA7UBGSWEK3OBXGRNAO7CPHIMF4%2F&h=048e4efc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200215/A7UBGSWEK3OBXGRNAO7CPHIMF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n藥房訛稱生理鹽水可消毒  兩人被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200215/large/1581697784_ec0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200215%2Flarge%2F1581697784_ec0b.jpg&h=0066cf09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角一間藥房聲稱出售的生理鹽水可洗手拖地。海關提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】不法商人藉武漢肺炎肆虐發災難財，海關前日派員「放蛇」，搗破旺角一間藥房以不良手法售賣生理鹽水，聲稱可洗手和拖地，涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》。藥房一名董事及一名店員被捕。<br />\n<br />\n海關早前於1月27日展開代號「守護者」行動，巡查全港各區外科口罩及防疫產品的零售點。前日海關派員喬裝顧客到旺角一間藥房試買，發現涉案藥房出售以膠樽裝載、標示為「0.9% sodium chloride」（氯化鈉）及「清洗傷口用」 的生理鹽水，每樽1,000毫升售價25元，五樽100元；載貨紙箱上更展示自製單張，聲稱生理鹽水「適用於洗手、清潔，可拖地」，涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生指不能殺菌<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港家居隔離者擅往公院求診<br />\n<br />\n關員隨即拘捕該藥房一名30歲店員，其後再拘捕另一名30歲藥房董事。行動中海關共撿獲23支生理鹽水，市值近600元，並會將這批生理鹽水送往政府化驗所化驗，確定成份及安全性，案件有待調查。截至前日為止，持續18天的「守護者」行動期間，海關出動超過1,900人在全港各區零售點巡查超過12,000次。<br />\n<br />\n生理鹽水是含0.9%氯化鈉的無菌水劑，與人類體液濃度相近，是常用清洗劑，不刺激傷口，引起較少痛楚。家庭醫生鄭志文指出，生理鹽水常用於清洗傷口或洗眼，一般沒有細菌感染的傷口，可使用生理鹽水清洗。他稱生理鹽水不能消毒殺菌，亦不宜於今次疫症中大量使用以洗手及拖地。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛"},{"pid":"0c6a698fc5db1c1b06c8eb6b617535550ee487b5","tid":1880593,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"經過左六個月 應該係人都知唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474fd76efa1eda92981b489eeafacb9add1f753e","tid":1880593,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c6a698fc5db1c1b06c8eb6b617535550ee487b5","tid":1880593,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"經過左六個月 應該係人都知唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"藍屍咪唔知"},{"pid":"2f030651159c57b6d8286cb44b678e2f21826992","tid":1880593,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c6a698fc5db1c1b06c8eb6b617535550ee487b5","tid":1880593,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"經過左六個月 應該係人都知唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"8個月喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9698e7ac6c1ea200924412ed41e89623ec17b34","tid":1880593,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"474fd76efa1eda92981b489eeafacb9add1f753e","tid":1880593,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c6a698fc5db1c1b06c8eb6b617535550ee487b5","tid":1880593,"uid":46042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"經過左六個月 應該係人都知唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:27:29.000Z","msg":"藍屍咪唔知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"Aggrr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a489183f547bfb52f66aa8626a190cb7c7ec75de","tid":1880593,"uid":348550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T03:29:22.000Z","msg":"咁公平啲講佢淨係話可以洗手拖地咋嘛，係得㗎喎，清水都得豉油都得㗎，殺唔到呢隻病毒咁解咋嘛，佢又冇話可以殺到病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}